<!--
  Legacy staff directory.  Exported from the pre-acquisition HR system and
  never migrated into the users table.  The admin "Staff directory" search
  (routes/admin.js -> GET /admin/directory) queries this file with an XPath
  expression built by string-concatenating the ?name= parameter.

  VULN (B-INJ-XPATH): XPath injection.  The api_token and clearance fields
  are meant to be invisible to the directory UI (the template only prints
  name/title/email), but an injected predicate such as  ' or '1'='1  selects
  every <employee> node and a blind substring() oracle reads any field.
-->
